---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="页面未找到 | 创作工具导航" description="页面不存在或已移动。">
  <main class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <section class="max-w-xl text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-600">404</p>
      <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold text-gray-950 dark:text-gray-50">页面未找到</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">这个页面可能已经移动，回到首页继续查看创作工具、SEO 工具和文本处理资源。</p>
      <a class="mt-8 inline-flex rounded-full bg-gray-950 px-5 py-3 text-white dark:bg-gray-50 dark:text-gray-950" href="/">返回首页</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
